  "title": "*Urgent* 5 Months Contract Procurement Asisstant (Education Sector) - East (up to $2500) #NJE",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist with Procurement Tender function - Such as scheduling project meetings during the tender stage, site show rounds, tender clarifications, seamless information  collaboration between internal and external stakeholders, tender closing and generating management reports for approval.</li><li>Assist in resolving supply, quality, service, and invoicing issues between Suppliers and internal stakeholders</li><li>Assist and guide requestors to ensure that all requirements and scope of works are clearly defined before sourcing from the market</li><li>Assist with the preparation of ad hoc tender and administrative paperwork (e.g. Drafting of Invitation to  tender, preparing letter of award, etc.) </li><li>Assist with any other duties, tasks or jobs with similar levels of responsibility and complexity to the assigned job grade as may be reasonably requested</li></ul><p>Joy Yeow Zhi Qian<br />(CEI Registration No:R2096261)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA Licence No: 99C4599)</p>",
